	* From Mattias Helsing, "Replace the IF(POLICY CMP0008) with an
	  absolute version check for
	  cmake > 2.6.0.
	  The POLICY keyword is only valid starting with cmake-2.4.7 so
	  using it
	  broke cmake 2.4.5/6 support."

