	  look at the problem.
	  Attached is a change that is able to provide shared textures for
	  the clamp and
	  the repeat case.
	  So this appears to be the best fix I guess ...
	  
	  Also it additionaly shares the TexEnv StateAttribute in a whole
	  ac3d model."

