	* From Mathias Froehlich, "This change makes the net plugin compile
	  on hp-ux.
	  It tries to unify some partly ugly ifdefs in the socket classes.
	  The change is also tested on a solaris 8, irix 6.5 and suse 9.0
	  machine."

