2007-05-21 08:01  robert

	* From Olaf Flebbe, "FlightGear/OSG on Windows did not load the
	  Texture Fonts.
	  
	  1) TXF Fonts are binary.
	  2) Do not rely on the result of istream::readsome if buffer _is_
	  empty
	  and no data have been read before."

