	  purposes.

2005-09-19 15:33  robert

	* From Mike Weiblen: support for OSGHANGGLIDE_REVERSE_CONTROLS env
	  which reverses
	  the pitch and roll control to account from Mike's "unique" way of
	  flying hang gliders :-)

