	* Fix for OSX build across both Tiger and 10.3.x

2005-05-05 20:05  robert

	* Removed rgb alias for Quicktime mapping since the Quicktime is
	  not reliable
	  at loading all rgb files that the standard OSG rgb reader can
	  read.

