	* CHanged line 101 in PageLOD.cpp to read
	  if ( in->getVersion() >= VERSION_0006 ) {
	  setDatabasePath(in->readString());
	  }
	  
	  instead of
	  if ( in->getVersion() > VERSION_0006 ) {
	  setDatabasePath(in->readString());
	  }
	  
	  Seems DatabasePath _is_ present in ive files of version 6.

