	* Made the Professional services subscript optional - use "osglogo
	  ps" to enable
	  it.

2003-02-11 12:37  robert

	* Clean up of the logo demo.

2003-02-10 22:15  don

	* Used INC instead of CXXFLAGS
	  
	  GVS:
	  ----------------------------------------------------------------------

